snippet.title: Wittle Mistakes Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2798430/Wittle_Mistakes_Prologue/

Play our Indie Baby Game 👶
Wittle Mistakes is a mechanics-based third-person 3D adventure game where players navigate the trials of infancy within the Mother Corporation. Engage in creative puzzle-solving, master intricate platforming, and unveil the dark secrets that Mother has been hiding. The playpen awaits.
